title: Down Syndrome, Speech delay, Treatment Therapy Pack 4
description:
Down Syndrome (DS) Treatment and Therapy pack FOUR

(third try, reupload)

Many items proven to help kids with DS (and that have helped my kid!).

THIS PACK is pack 4: non ISO Video Files

1) Targeted Nutritional Intervention for Down Syndrome

2) Oral Motor Therapy videos for Down Syndrome or low tone

3) Communication and Speech Therapy videos for all kids at risk of speech delay


Please see packs 1 and 2 for

Sound Therapy to help sensory processing and working memory

Music Therapy (Mozart) to raise Growth Hormone and speed healing

Breastfeeding help for infants with DS

e-Books of natural treatments and supplements

and Pack 3 for more videos in ISO format. 




These approaches are best if used together
